        "type": "SHMEM_LIMIT_MISMATCH",
        "description": "Measured max shared memory per block (101376 bytes) differs from API-reported (49152 bytes). The probe successfully enabled opt-in extended shared memory via cudaFuncSetAttribute, or the API is reporting a virtualised/restricted value.",
        "expected": 49152,
